---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import ParallaxBanner from '../../components/ParallaxBanner.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Canyon Lake Neighborhoods | Cody Posey Real Estate"
  description="Explore Canyon Lake neighborhoods — from lakefront gated communities to Hill Country acreage. Find the right area for your lifestyle and budget."
>
  <Navbar />
  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="cl-hero">
      <div class="cl-hero__overlay"></div>
      <div class="cl-hero__content">
        <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="/canyon-lake/">Canyon Lake</a> <span>/</span> <span>Neighborhoods</span>
        </nav>
        <h1>Canyon Lake <span style="color:#FF1616;">Neighborhoods</span></h1>
        <p>Lakefront communities, gated estates, and Hill Country acreage</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="cl-page-intro cl-page-intro--centered">Canyon Lake is organized around a mix of lakefront and off-lake communities, each with a distinct character. Whether you want direct waterfront access, a gated neighborhood with resort-style amenities, or a quiet homesite on acreage with Hill Country views — there's an area here that fits.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Neighborhoods -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--light-gray);">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Canyon Lake <span class="accent">Communities</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="cl-neighborhood__grid">
          <div class="cl-neighborhood__card">
            <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/cl-canyon-lake-hills.png" alt="Canyon Lake Hills homes" class="cl-neighborhood__img" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>Canyon Lake Hills</h3>
            <p>An established, active community with waterfront on three sides, Canyon Lake Hills offers a peaceful, rural, lake-centric lifestyle. Amenities include a swimming pool, children's park, tennis courts, and a boat ramp. The neighborhood features a mix of full-time residents and vacation homes.</p>
            <div class="cl-neighborhood__tags">
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">$300K - $800K</span>
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">Comal ISD</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cl-neighborhood__card">
            <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/cl-mystic-shores.png" alt="Mystic Shores homes" class="cl-neighborhood__img" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>Mystic Shores</h3>
            <p>Nestled between the Guadalupe River and the north shore of Canyon Lake, Mystic Shores offers a tranquil, luxurious Hill Country lifestyle. Resort-like amenities include a community center, multiple pools, walking trails, sports courts, and parks. Properties range from 1 to 20+ acres with water or Hill Country views.</p>
            <div class="cl-neighborhood__tags">
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">$350K - $700K</span>
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">Comal ISD</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cl-neighborhood__card">
            <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/cl-oak-shores.png" alt="Oak Shores Estates homes" class="cl-neighborhood__img" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>Oak Shores Estates</h3>
            <p>An exclusive gated lakefront community on the south side of Canyon Lake, Oak Shores Estates features crystal-clear water views and custom homes on generous lots. Amenities include a homeowner's park with playscape and pool. The neighborhood is predominantly full-time residents.</p>
            <div class="cl-neighborhood__tags">
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">$500K - $4M+</span>
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">Comal ISD</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cl-neighborhood__card">
            <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/cl-canyon-lake-estates.png" alt="Canyon Lake Estates homes" class="cl-neighborhood__img" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>Canyon Lake Estates</h3>
            <p>A well-established community around Canyon Lake, Canyon Lake Estates offers homeowner amenities including a pool and regular community events. The neighborhood features various home styles set among established landscaping, providing an accessible entry point to lake-area living.</p>
            <div class="cl-neighborhood__tags">
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">$250K - $500K</span>
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">Comal ISD</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cl-neighborhood__card">
            <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/cl-hancock.png" alt="Hancock Area homes" class="cl-neighborhood__img" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>Hancock Area</h3>
            <p>Properties along Hancock Road in the historical Hancock Canyon area, which takes its name from the original Hancock community that was submerged when Canyon Lake was created in the 1960s. The area maintains a rural character with individual properties and land parcels.</p>
            <div class="cl-neighborhood__tags">
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">$200K - $400K</span>
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">Comal ISD</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cl-neighborhood__card">
            <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/cl-river-mountain-ranch.png" alt="River Mountain Ranch homes" class="cl-neighborhood__img" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>River Mountain Ranch</h3>
            <p>A luxurious acreage community along the Guadalupe River, River Mountain Ranch offers serene country living on spacious private lots. Residents enjoy two gated river parks with hiking, grilling, and river access for kayaking, tubing, and fishing. The community is horse-friendly, making it ideal for buyers seeking both space and a riverfront lifestyle.</p>
            <div class="cl-neighborhood__tags">
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">$400K - $800K</span>
              <span class="cl-neighborhood__tag">Comal ISD</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- School District -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>School <span class="accent">District</span></h2>
          <p>Canyon Lake is served by one of the top-rated districts in the region</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cl-schools__grid">
          <a href="https://www.comalisd.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cl-schools__card">
            <h3>Comal ISD</h3>
            <p>One of the fastest-growing and highest-rated districts in Texas. Comal ISD serves the entire Canyon Lake area with multiple elementary, middle, and high school campuses.</p>
            <span class="cl-schools__link">Visit Comal ISD Website →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section" style="background: #000; color: #fff; text-align: center;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need Help <span class="accent">Narrowing It Down</span>?</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem;">I can walk you through the differences between Canyon Lake communities and help you focus your search on neighborhoods that match your priorities.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get Help Choosing a Neighborhood</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <ParallaxBanner image="/images/generated/canyon-lake-water.png" />

  <ContactForm context="I'd like to learn more about Canyon Lake neighborhoods..." />
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .cl-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 280px;
    background: url('/images/generated/canyon-lake-water.png') center/cover no-repeat;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .cl-hero__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
  }

  .cl-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .cl-hero__content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cl-hero__content p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .breadcrumb span {
    margin: 0 0.3rem;
  }

  .cl-page-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .cl-page-intro--centered {
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--black);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Neighborhood Cards */
  .cl-neighborhood__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cl-neighborhood__card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cl-neighborhood__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .cl-neighborhood__card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    padding-right: 2rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cl-neighborhood__card p {
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    flex: 1;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  .cl-neighborhood__tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    padding-right: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cl-neighborhood__tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--light-gray);
    color: var(--gray);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  /* Schools */
  .cl-schools__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cl-schools__card {
    display: block;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cl-schools__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .cl-schools__card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #000;
  }

  .cl-schools__card:hover h3 {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .cl-schools__card p {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cl-schools__link {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cl-neighborhood__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
